Find all employees who are either in the 'Sales' department and earn over $70,000, OR are in the 'Engineering' department and were hired after 2022-01-01.

Solution:

SELECT 
first_name, 
employee_id 
FROM employees
WHERE ((department = 'Sales') AND (salary > 70000)) 
OR ((department = 'Engineering') AND (hire_date > '2022-01-01'))

